Mantis' Face Preset Collections

♡ All of my public face/head collections. Compatible with EOTB/Unique Tav. Body types 1 and 2 only for now.

Fallout London Downgrader and Addons

This mod includes the Fallout London Downgrader, which allows you to downgrade Fallout 4 with a few button clicks. It also includes various goodies that are required for modding Fallout London such as edited Fallout 4 master files, source scripts, recommended mods and more.

Fallout London Downgrader and Addons

Author: TeamFOLON

This mod includes the Fallout London Downgrader, which allows you to downgrade Fallout 4 with a few button clicks. It also includes various goodies that are required for modding Fallout London such as edited Fallout 4 master files, source scripts, recommended mods and more.

Fallout Vault 13 - Demo

Author: Fallout Vault 13 Development Team

Uploader: fallout4vault13

Fallout: Vault 13 is a total conversion mod for Fallout 4 that remakes and reimagines Fallout 1 in Fallout 4's engine. This demo features the entirety of "The Inyo", the first major open-world area in Fallout: Vault 13.

Rabbit's REAL LIGHTS New Atlantis

Author: RabbitDoesStuff

Uploader: RabbitDoesStuff

Rabbit's Real Lights: New Atlantis is a New Atlantis Lighting Overhaul. Adds over 300+ hand placed light sources and several tweaks for realism and better visibility at nighttime! Enjoy the city under the stars in its real light glory!

High Poly Children

High Poly Children is a complete overhaul of Skyrim children, giving them new looks, races, clothes and more! Optionally, it allows child races to be fully functional and playable.

High Poly Children

Dry Wells - Legion Expansion

Lore-friendly quest & land expansion with 20+ quests, 35+ fully voiced characters, new minor factions, a player home, and multiple main questlines. Allows the player to visit Dry Wells before nuking it in Lonesome Road, and expands upon Legion lands in Arizona. ~6 hours of content, with expansive player choice and consequences.

Carrots Remade - New Carrot HD textures and meshes

Just a new mesh and texture for carrots. Textures are actually 2k/1k. Mesh is low poly so no performance impact.
